  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 400 degrees.",
    "Roll out the puff pastry and cut into 4 equal pieces.",
    "Spread a layer of garlic sauce on each piece of pastry.",
    "Top the garlic sauce with a layer of ground lamb.",
    "Sprinkle crumbly feta cheese over the lamb.",
    "Add a layer of kalamata olives, artichoke hearts, and sun dried tomatoes.",
    "Sprinkle chopped fresh parsley over the top.",
    "Bake the flatbreads in the oven for 20 minutes.",
    "Remove the flatbreads from the oven and let cool for 5 minutes.",
    "Serve the flatbreads on a lazy-susan-spinner for easy sharing."
